<HEADLINE> UNAM 0, Cruz Azul 0  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   DALLAS (AP) -- UNAM and Cruz Azul played to a 0-0 tie, and
Atlante defeated Atlas 2-1 in the Copa Pre-Libertadores round-robin
soccer matches between Mexican professional clubs Wednesday night
at the Cotton Bowl.
</P>
<P>
   Cruz Azul was stopped on several scoring chances, missing on all
10 shots on goal.
</P>
<P>
   Jose Manuel Abundis scored both goals for Atlante.
</P>
<P>
   The Copa Pre-Libertadores tournament continues in Los Angeles on
Aug. 9, and concludes in Fresno, Calif., Sept. 6. Through
round-robin play, two Mexican clubs will qualify for the 2000 Copa
Libertadores, an annual tournament in which top teams from 10 South
American nations compete.
</P>
