nine points during that stretch to complete its comeback.
</P>
<P>
   Williams had a 3-pointer and a fast-break layup, and Thompson
added a 3-pointer and two free throws as Indiana used a 9-2 run to
break from a 23-all tie to a 34-25 lead 4:42 before halftime.
</P>
<P>
   The Fever led 44-35 at the half.
